# get the current masses of the bodies (num_assets, num_bodies)
masses = self.asset.root_physx_view.get_masses()


# set the mass into the physics simulation
self.asset.root_physx_view.set_masses(masses, env_ids)


# all tensors are CPU
root_physx_view: omni.physics.tensors.impl.api.ArticulationView 说明是isaacsim的API，实际上抄的是isaacsim的rigidprim的API，不是articulation的